OL,3,CMan accused of keeping dead father in
OL,4,Cfreezer denied bail
OL,6,FSome readers may find the content of
OL,7,Fthis article distressing.
OL,9,FA man accused of keeping his dead
OL,10,Ffather in a freezer in the family home
OL,11,Fhas been remanded in custody.
OL,13,FJohn Garrett O'Sullivan, 55, appeared
OL,14,Fbefore a judge in Londonderry
OL,15,FMagistrates' Court on Monday morning
OL,16,Fcharged with attempting to prevent the
OL,17,Flawful burial of his father, 86-year-
OL,18,Fold Noel O'Sullivan.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/19
