OL,3,CMan accused of keeping dead father in
OL,4,Cfreezer denied bail
OL,6,FThe court heard that the pensioner's
OL,7,Fremains were found in the living room
OL,8,Fof the house on the Culmore Road in
OL,9,FDerry wrapped in plastic sheeting and
OL,10,Fa duvet.
OL,12,FHis head was placed inside an open
OL,13,Ffridge freezer while the rest of his
OL,14,Fbody lay on the floor beside the open
OL,15,Fdoor of another freezer.
OL,17,FDeputy district judge Philip Mateer
OL,18,Fremanded John O'Sullivan in custody as
OL,19,Fhe expressed concerns about the state
OL,20,Fof his mental health.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/19
