OL,6,FThe accused, who is unemployed but has
OL,7,Fa PhD in electrical engineering,
OL,8,Fappeared via video-link from a police
OL,9,Fcustody suite.
OL,11,FO'Sullivan, who lived at the family
OL,12,Fhome on Culmore Road with his father,
OL,13,Falbeit at times residing in the
OL,14,Fgarage, spoke briefly at the outset of
OL,15,Fthe hearing to confirm his date of
OL,16,Fbirth and that he understood the
OL,17,Fcharge facing him.
