OL,3,CMan accused of keeping dead father in
OL,4,Cfreezer denied bail
OL,6,FHe is accused of attempting to prevent
OL,7,Fthe lawful and decent burial of his
OL,8,Ffather on dates between July 1 and
OL,9,FJuly 17.
OL,11,FOutlining the circumstances of the
OL,12,Fcase, a detective constable told the
OL,13,Fcourt that officers received a report
OL,14,Ffrom one of Noel O'Sullivan's
OL,15,Fdaughters on Wednesday July 17
OL,16,Fexpressing concern that she was unable
OL,17,Fto contact her father or gain entry to
OL,18,Fthe house. On arrival, police forced
OL,19,Fentry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/19
