OL,6,F"On entering the property, officers
OL,7,Fhave reported that there was an odour
OL,8,Fof human remains," the officer told
OL,9,Fthe judge.
OL,11,F"On entering the living room, police
OL,12,Fobserved a duvet leading into a fridge
OL,13,Ffreezer which was turned on and
OL,14,Frunning with a second fridge freezer
OL,15,Flocated next to it.
OL,17,F"Police began to remove the layers of
OL,18,Fduvet to reveal a plastic sheet. On
OL,19,Fremoving this, human remains of Mr
OL,20,FNoel O'Sullivan were located.
