OL,6,F"The body of Mr Noel O'Sullivan
OL,7,Fappeared to be lying for some time. It
OL,8,Fwas wrapped in clear tarpaulin
OL,9,Fplastic. There was an adult nappy on
OL,10,Fhis head and hands. He was also
OL,11,Fwrapped in dry night bedding with a
OL,12,Fwet wipe type cloth inserted into his
OL,13,Fmouth.
OL,15,F"The deceased's head was placed into
OL,16,Fthe fridge freezer and his body was
OL,17,Fsurrounded by the open door of a
OL,18,Fsecond fridge."
