OL,6,FJohn O'Sullivan was arrested later
OL,7,Fthat day when he was found walking on
OL,8,Fthe Culmore Road toward the house.
OL,10,FHe was initially detained on suspicion
OL,11,Fof murder but later re-arrested on a
OL,12,Fcharge of attempting to prevent a
OL,13,Flawful burial.
OL,15,FThe court heard that the results of a
OL,16,Fpost-mortem examination on his father
OL,17,Fhad been "inconclusive".
OL,26,@yD@JOUyD@WO]
