OL,6,FHe claimed that his father was, at
OL,7,Ftimes, having difficulty breathing but
OL,8,Fwas also being abusive toward him.
OL,10,FHe said he left the room due to the
OL,11,Fabuse being directed at him and went
OL,12,Fto bed and, when he returned in the
OL,13,Flate afternoon of the same day, he
OL,14,Ffound his father dead.
OL,16,F"On the death of his father, he
OL,17,Fdescribed that he did not contact the
OL,18,Fauthorities as it was a bank holiday
OL,19,Fweekend," said the officer.
